      "writtenOn": "2026-05-26T09:17:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "question: is this range format understood by mirror backends?\n\nNot sure how ranges are repesented, but in case it is from `c123` to `c456`, will mongo be able to return the entry if `c200` is used as a filter?\n\nMaybe we need to change the way range is represented?",
